gov.ncbi.pmc.dtdanalyzer

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ncbi.pmc.dtdanalyzer.Element

  • public class Element
extends Object
    Holds all the information associated with an element declaration in the DTD. Class does not hold any attribute information, but this can be accessed through the Attribute and Attributes classes. Element also provides no "context" information (ie, the places where a given element can occur), but this information is available through the ModelBuilder class.
    Author:
    Demian Hess
